### Dataverse Web API examples (use VS Code REST Client or Postman)

# Create a Lead
POST https://{org}.crm.dynamics.com/api/data/v9.2/leads
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "subject": "Website contact",
  "firstname": "Alex",
  "lastname": "Smith",
  "emailaddress1": "alex.smith@example.com",
  "hmz_utm_source": "google",
  "hmz_utm_medium": "cpc",
  "hmz_utm_campaign": "summer_sale",
  "hmz_consentstatus": 1,
  "hmz_leadscore": 25
}

### Update Lead score
PATCH https://{org}.crm.dynamics.com/api/data/v9.2/leads({lead_guid})
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{ "hmz_leadscore": 60 }

### Query high-intent segment candidates
GET https://{org}.crm.dynamics.com/api/data/v9.2/leads?$select=fullname,hmz_leadscore,hmz_utm_source&$filter=hmz_leadscore ge 70
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
